Receiving Donations in DRIMS

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Click DRIMS in the sidebar, then select Donations

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,500
View the list of all donations for your warehouses

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Look for donations with Announced status and click to open

5
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:17,000
View donation details including incident, warehouse, donor, and status

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,500
Click Mark Received when physical goods arrive at your warehouse

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Fill in the received date and actual quantities

8
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,500
Click Confirm to save the received status

9
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,000
The donation status changes to Received

10
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,000
Click Inspect to check the quality and condition of items

11
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Check each item condition, quantity match, and quality

12
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,500
Click Complete Inspection when done checking all items

13
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,500
Click Stock to add inspected items to your warehouse inventory

14
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,500
Review the stock receipt showing items and quantities to add

15
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,000
Click Validate to confirm adding items to inventory

16
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:45,500
The donation is now Stocked and items are in your inventory

17
